witch_first_tribute_album.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" alt="" class="wp-image-122677"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 奥古斯塔办公室有限公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>`` <strong>SUKIMASWITCH 20周年纪念专辑《Everyone&#39;s Sukima Switch》</strong>将收录11位与Sukima Switch相关或尊重Sukima Switch的艺术家，他们将翻唱Sukima Switch的他们留下美好回忆的歌曲。星町水成将参与《<strong>黄金时光恋人</strong>》的封面。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="SUKIMASWITCH - “GOLDEN TIME RUBBER”音乐视频：SUKIMASWITCH / GOLDEN TIME RUBBER 音乐视频" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0iAF8TJAqp4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[星町水成] Golden Time Lover / Sukima Switch (钢之炼金术师) [歌曲框架剪切] (2021/03/08) 星町水成" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/enOyi_cDLJM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p> 《SUKIMASWITCH 20周年纪念专辑‘大家的Sukima Switch’》预定于5月29日发行。 </p><p></p><div class="kaerebalink-box" style="text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;font-size:small;zoom: 1;overflow: hidden;"><div class="kaerebalink-image" style="float:left;margin:0 15px 10px 0